**Senior citizen FD rates** are 0.25–0.75% higher than general public rates at most Indian banks. This extra interest can significantly increase maturity value over a 3–5 year FD. Additionally, senior citizens enjoy TDS-free interest up to ₹50,000 per year (vs ₹40,000 for others) and can claim ₹50,000 deduction under Section 80TTB.
